OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine, turning
OL,7,Fcloudier at times during the night
OL,8,Fwith perhaps some patchy rain for the
OL,9,Fnorth and the Hebrides by dawn. Light
OL,10,Fnortherly winds turning southerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with some light rain
OL,13,Ffor the Hebrides and far north
OL,14,Fotherwise dry with some bright spells.
OL,15,FA few afternoon showers developing in
OL,16,Fthe light westerly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
