OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,6,Fcloudy and showery start to the the
OL,7,Fnew week but conditions improving
OL,8,Flater on Monday. Light winds and a mix
OL,9,Fof cloud and brighter spells
OL,10,Fcontinuing towards mid week.
